The recommended PHP class is:

  https://gitorious.org/services_libravatar


Testing
--------

Clone the module under ~/devel/remote/services_libravatar:

  cd ~/devel/remote/
  git clone git://gitorious.org/services_libravatar/services_libravatar.git

Then put the test page under /var/www and create this symlink:

  ln -s ~/devel/remote/services_libravatar/Services /var/www/
